gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 131, Spurs 106
gameRecap.excerpt: Phoenix defeats San Antonio, 131-106. For Phoenix, Devin Booker led the way with 32 points, seven rebounds, and nine assists while Kevin Durant added 25 points, four rebounds, four assists, and three steals in the win. Keldon Johnson finished with 14 points and four rebounds with Victor Wembanyama tallying 13 points, five rebounds, and four assists for San Antonio in the losing effort. Phoenix improves to 42-29, while San Antonio moves to 15-56 in the loss.
